The '''2014 Open de Nice Côte d'Azur''' was a men's [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Clay court|outdoor clay courts]]. It was the 30th edition of the [[Open de Nice Côte d'Azur]] and was part of the [[ATP World Tour 250 series]] of the [[2014 ATP World Tour]]. It took place at the [[Nice Lawn Tennis Club]] in [[Nice]], [[France]], from May 18 through May 24, 2014.

