== Finals ==

=== Singles ===
{{main|2014 Open de Nice Côte d'Azur&nbsp;– Singles}}
*{{flagicon|LAT}} [[Ernests Gulbis]] defeated {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Federico Delbonis]], 6–1, 7–6<sup>(7–5)</sup>

=== Doubles ===
{{main|2014 Open de Nice Côte d'Azur&nbsp;– Doubles}}
*{{flagicon|SVK}} [[Martin Kližan]] / {{flagicon|AUT}} [[Philipp Oswald]] defeated {{flagicon|IND}} [[Rohan Bopanna]] / {{flagicon|PAK}} [[Aisam-ul-Haq Qureshi]], 6–2, 6–0

